com.aerospike.helper.query

Class Qualifier

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aerospike.helper.query.Qualifier
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Map<String,Object>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ExpiryQualifier, GenerationQualifier, KeyQualifier, TTLQualifier

    public class Qualifier
extends Object
implements Map<String,Object>
    Generic Bin qualifier. It acts as a filter to exclude records that do not met this criteria. The operations supported are
  • EQ - Equals
  • GT - Greater than
  • GTEQ - Greater than or equal to
  • LT - Less than
  • LTEQ - Less than or equal to
  • NOTEQ - Not equal
  • BETWEEN - Between two value (inclusive)
  • START_WITH - A string that starts with
  • ENDS_WITH - A string that ends with
Author:
peter
